summary:
- Chair Department Marketing and Supply Chain Management at the Faculty of Management. The primary representative of this academic discipline. Supervising and fostering the development of professionals;

- Contact person for Education, Research and Indirect funding of the Department Marketing and Supply Chain Management

- Associate Dean Education (for 3 programmes: 2 MSc and 1 BSc: Faculty of Management.

- Supervising up to twenty Master of Science theses and four PhD theses;
- working on quality assurance, courses, articles, commercial programs;
for the Faculty Management, Science & Technology and the Open Universiteit;
- networking in diverse areas of expertise.

Member of the International Purchasing and Supply Management Education and Research Association

Specialties: Supply Chain Management, Logistics, (Electronic) Customer Relationship Management (CRM), Supplier development, Multilevel analyses, Structural Equation Modelling, Japan
